  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Current Pool:&nbsp;</strong>[[(round(@classes.eidolon.level * .75))]]</p>\n<p>The value given in this column is the total number of points in the eidolon's evolution pool. Points from this pool can be spent on a wide variety of modifications and upgrades that add new abilities, attacks, and powers to the eidolon.</p>\n<p>Whenever the summoner gains a level, the number in this pool increases and the summoner can spend these points to change the abilities of the eidolon. These choices are not set.</p>\n<p>The summoner can change them whenever he gains a level (and through the transmogrify spell).</p>\n<p><strong>Usage</strong></p>\n<p>Subtract from the total when adding evolutions.</p>",
